Jeremy Bailys

Location
New York, NY


Business Segment

Global Market Strategies




Jeremy Bailys is a Senior Associate in the Carlyle GMS Finance Group.  He is based in New York.
Prior to joining Carlyle, Mr. Bailys was an investment banking analyst and associate at Wells Fargo Securities in the Industrials Group.
Mr. Bailys graduated from the University of Florida with a Masters of Science in Finance and a B.A. in Finance.












































