        Skip to main navigation
      










Search

























 


Team









 










Pranai Cheroo

Location
New York, NY


Business Segment

Global Market Strategies




Pranai Cheroo is a Senior Associate in the Carlyle GMS Finance group, focusing on underwriting and portfolio management. He is based in New York.
Prior to joining Carlyle, Mr. Cheroo was a Senior Associate at Summit Partners, where he focused on originating and managing credit investments. Prior to his time at Summit, he worked in the Merchant Banking and Loan Syndications groups at BNP Paribas.
Mr. Cheroo holds a BA in quantitative economics and mathematics from Tufts University.












































Dan Cohn-Sfetcu | The Carlyle Group














